textBeforeTable: Project info 2010-05-21 Project enters incubation. 2012-04-20 Project is retired. News ATTENTION: Apache Zeta Components has retired from incubation and left the Apache Software Foundation for various reasons. You can find the project on their new home at github: http://github.com/zetacomponents. Zeta Components is a high-quality library of loosely-coupled PHP components. Description The Zeta Components project retired on 2012-04-20 This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general project status, look on the project website.
